name: Araçari-Banana
description:
The Araçari-Banana(Pteroglossus bailloni) is bird of the Ramphastidae family (same from the Toucans) found in the Atlantic Forest, south-eastern Brazil. Art made with pastel crayons and digital editing.

Respect and take care of nature.
